568
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:34,600
Your Majesty.

569
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:44,480
♪The road to Chang'an shrouded in mist♪

570
00:39:48,040 --> 00:39:48,680
Your Majesty.

571
00:39:51,398 --> 00:39:58,140
♪I unknowingly learn of your affection♪

572
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:02,000
Your Majesty, don't be sad.
Your Majesty!

573
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:11,522
♪To stay or to leave, you decide♪

574
00:40:11,523 --> 00:40:15,060
♪Nations are different♪

575
00:40:15,546 --> 00:40:20,820
♪One without desire
is one that is not alive♪

576
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:24,711
♪Looking at the sky side by side♪

577
00:40:24,712 --> 00:40:28,500
♪We've gotten closer with time♪

578
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:34,420
♪One glance,
the city of Chang'an is bare♪

579
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:42,380
♪Among the ridiculous people
